I" <h4 id="exercise-5-type-in-motion">Exercise 5: Type in Motion</h4>
<p>Find a short bit of spoken audio. The audio could be from a movie, tv show, speech, etc. but should not have much background noise (so no music). Make a short animation that has the words come on and off screen timed to the audio track.</p>

<h5 id="technical-requirements">Technical Requirements</h5>
<ul>
  <li>1920x1080</li>
  <li>Somewhere between 5 and 15 seconds</li>
  <li>Uses audio</li>
</ul>

